HEADWORD: Balearic
<hw>Bal`e*ar"ic</hw> <pr>(b⟦acr⟧l`⟦esl⟧*⟦acr⟧r"⟦icr⟧k)</pr>,
<pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>Balearicus</ets>, fr. Gr.
